title: Various Artists - Navigator's Fresh!! Indie Playlist June 201
description:
Hello friends,

Thanks for your continuos support!NAVIGATOR team wishes to thank all the people who keep downloading our lists.There's more and more of you each month, and we're trying hard to choose only quality stuff and include it in our playlist and make it more FRESH!!! each time.

Anyone who is interested in sending your own stuff (via links to downloads), we would gladly listen to your music and include it in our list or radio show if we find it good, so more people would hear it...

This month we proudly present acoustic band IKA from Serbia which is having it's debut album released later in june. Soon we will post some more lists with our choice of music in other genres as well - ranging from fresh electronic to fresh jazz,swing,nu soul & groove and more...

As always, our own radio show is on the internet radio station(every Tuesday 9pm CET).There you will be able to hear some new stuff before we upload it on the net.

We also included artwork from our good friend Andrea Rankovic. Every month you will be able to use her artwork as cover for Navigator's Fresh!! Indie Playlists.


Best regards
Navigator team


P.s. of course, if you like the music, support the artists and buy it!

NAVIGATOR, music team producing beats,grooves and much more...And an awesome DJ team and a soundsystem as well proudly presents:

NAVIGATOR FRESH!! INDIE PLAYLIST JUNE 2010

NAVIGATOR FRESH!! INDIE PLAYLIST contains the team's choice when it comes to independent music acts,ranging from guitar, acts to so called "indietronica" and experimental sounds...
Enjoy!
